# 🔹 9. GREEDY

### 🧠 When to Use

* Local optimal works globally

### ⚙️ Algorithm

```
1. Sort (if needed)
2. Pick best option at each step
3. Move forward
```

### ⚠️ Notes

* Doesn’t work for all problems
* Validate with examples

