# 🔹 10. HEAP (PRIORITY QUEUE)

### 🧠 When to Use

* Top K problems
* Min / Max element repeatedly

### ⚙️ Algorithm

```
1. Build heap
2. Push / pop elements
3. Maintain size if needed
```

