# 🔥 FINAL: PROBLEM DECISION FLOW

```
1. Contiguous? → Sliding Window
2. Sum problems? → Prefix Sum + HashMap
3. Sorted / pairs? → Two Pointer
4. Shortest path? → BFS
5. All possibilities? → Backtracking
6. Repeating work? → DP
7. Sorted search? → Binary Search
```

